     H            Y.
     F** UEXR05A *******************************************
     F*  EXSUB - CHECK OUTSOURCE PART                      *
     F*  J. WATANABE  2022.07.01                           *
     F*----------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UEXR05A'
     F*                    PARM           P@SHN  15
     F*                    PARM           P@OUTS  1
     F*                    PARM           P@DEPT  4
     F*  IN  P@SHN   15  IAF PART# (IF HYPHEN EXISTS --> REMOVE HYPHEN)
     F*  OUT P@OUTS   1  N=NOT OUTSRC, A=ASJ, O=OUTSRC
     F*      P@DEPT   4  DEPERTMENT
     F******************************************************
     E                    DPT        15  4
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *   PARAMETER TRANCEFER                              *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@SHN  15
     C                     PARM           P@OUTS  1
     C                     PARM           P@DEPT  4
     C                     MOVE 'N'       P@OUTS
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    P@DEPT
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * REMOVE HYPHEN
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     C                     MOVELP@SHN     $FLD1     P
     C                     CALL 'UUUR05'
     C                     PARM           $FLD1  25
     C                     PARM           $FLD2  25
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * MAIN ROUTINE
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     C                     MOVEL$FLD2     $SHIN
     C                     CALL 'UEXR05'
     C                     PARM           $SHIN  12
     C                     PARM           OUTBMN 60
     C                     PARM           OUTKBN 45
     C                     PARM           OUTTKR 90
     C                     PARM           OUTSHR 15
     C                     PARM           OUTKOT 45
     C                     PARM           OUTHBN180
     C                     PARM           STATUS  1
      *
     C                     MOVEAOUTBMN    DPT
     C           1         DO   15        IX      20
     C           DPT,IX    IFNE '0000'
     C           DPT,IX    ANDNE'0111'
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       P@OUTS
     C                     MOVE DPT,IX    P@DEPT
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C           P@OUTS    IFEQ 'Y'
     C           P@DEPT    IFEQ '8990'
     C                     MOVE 'A'       P@OUTS
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE 'O'       P@OUTS
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
